Participants have shared their takeaways from this year's World Economic Forum Annual Meeting with CGTN. Margery Kraus, founder and executive chair of APCO Worldwide, said it was inspiring to see people working on solutions to global challenges, and talking about them in a constructive way. Joe Ngai, chairman of McKinsey China, said that the meetings conveyed a lot of optimism over resilience and cooperation amid current uncertainties in the world.